data.comment: This is my second Any% run, but my first Any% submission, I wasn't happy with my first run (A 52:41:600), it had way too many dumb mistakes and deaths, but I am happier with this one, it is executed better. I hopefully will be trying to lower this time down, I need to get a better understanding of some of the chapters first though.

The Badeline fight felt pretty decent -- and Rescue was pretty good as well.
